  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The SYNCAT study intention is to study the level of adherence of the centers in Cataluña tu
      the Syncope Guidelines ESC2009 for the diagnosis and treatment of syncope and the impact that
      following them can have in the prognosis of these patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
